Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:14.33,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,如今你认为我写了成千上万首歌{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:19.07,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,不过是心受伤后得到的才能{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:24.44,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,但是每次提到你 话太多了说不完{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:28.17,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,而且我永远也不知从何开始{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:33.48,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,从那天起没人能替代你在我心中的位置{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:38.46,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,没人能补充你留下的空缺{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:43.23,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,我问我自己 还能再爱吗{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:47.66,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,还是害怕再受一次类似的打击{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:52.88,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,又一次打击 又一次疼痛{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:57.48,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,一个人能承受多少伤害{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:02.00,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,又一种害怕不能被我抹去{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:06.54,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,不过是想搞清一颗心能承受多少伤害{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:11.12,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,现在你觉得我应该让你走{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:16.44,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,这样我晚上就不会再梦到你{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:21.29,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,但我就是不能放下你{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:25.72,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,你怎能连打都不打一下就离开{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:30.43,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,你从未说过的那些话萦绕在我心头{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:35.32,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,你所做的则锋利得像把刀{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:40.27,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,我问我自己你有没有考虑过我的感受{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:44.19,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,当你慢慢回过神儿的时候{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:49.82,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,又一次打击 又一次疼痛{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:54.43,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,一个人能承受多少伤害{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:59.15,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,天哪 又一个伤口{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:03.21,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,一颗心能碎多少次{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:08.16,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,现在你觉得我会拿起电话{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.28,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,然后告诉你为啥我这么悲伤{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:18.49,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,但是每次提到你 话太多了说不完{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:22.59,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,听你说得太多了{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:27.34,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,听你说得太多了{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:40.16,LC中文歌词,,0,0,0,,听你说得太多了{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:14.33,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,By now you'd think I'd write a million songs{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:19.07,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,Gifts of a wounded heart{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:24.44,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to you, there's too much to say{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:28.17,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,And I never know where to start{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:33.48,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,Since that day no one had taken your place{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:38.46,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,No one can fill up the space you left behind{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:43.23,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,I ask myself, could I ever love again?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:47.66,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,And bear another beating of this kind?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:52.88,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,Another strike, another ache{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:57.48,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,How much hurt can one take?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:02.00,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,Another fear I cannot shake{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:06.54,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,Just how much hurt can one heart take?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:11.12,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,By now you think I would let you go{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:16.44,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,That I'd stop dreaming of you at night{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:21.29,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,But I just can't stop thinking about{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:25.72,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,How you walked away without a fight{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:30.43,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,The words you never said they haunt me{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:35.32,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,The one's you did were as sharp as a knife{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:40.27,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,I ask myself if you ever thought of me{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:44.19,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,While you were slowly coming back to life{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:49.82,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,Another strike, another ache{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:54.43,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,How much hurt can one take?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:59.15,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,Another scar, for heaven's sake{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:03.21,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,How many times can one heart break?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:08.16,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,By now you'd think I'd pick up the phone{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.28,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,And tell you I've been feeling so blue{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:18.49,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to you, there's too much to say{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:22.59,LC英文歌词,,0,0,0,,So much to be said by you{\fad(0,500)}
